						<summary>

						<p>On the inner <hi rend="italic">gōpura,</hi> right of entrance of the temple of Pālvaṇṇanāthasvāmi.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Vyaya, Chittirai 11, Anusha, Sunday.</hi></p>						

						<p>The Tamil record in verse may be palaeographically assigned to c. century. It registers the construction of the <hi rend="italic">gōpura</hi> of the temple of Pālvaṇṇanāthar.</p>						

